txt.en: Supplies can be found in Díngarth.\n\nYou should gather supplies.

'Yes, these supplies will be very helpful. Thank you for bringing them to me. The dwarf in charge of sending the supplies has been less than punctual in the past, and it is good to see he stalls no longer.\n\n'I commend your efforts, and his. Good day to you.'

'The name is Skirfir, and I keep track of supplies here in Díngarth. It keeps me busy enough.

'King Amroth has sent a list of various items needed at the encampment of Echad-in-Edhil. If you are heading that way, perhaps you could take them with you? And if not, well, I can find someone else, but I will not be happy about it! I know you are going that way, if not today then tomorrow. Look, do me a favour, will you?

'I can show you where to look to find everything that Amroth needs.'
Bring the supplies to Amroth in Echad-in-Edhil
The encampment of Echad-in-Edhil is in need of additional supplies.
Amroth can be found in Echad-in-Edhil.\n\nYou should bring the gathered supplies to Amroth.
'King Amroth has sent a list of various items needed at the encampment.'
